edu.udel.cis.vsl.sarl.prove.cvc

Class Translation

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.udel.cis.vsl.sarl.prove.cvc.Translation

  • public class Translation
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used to deal with div or modulo during the cvc translation Since cvc4 currently can not deal with div or modulo, div or modulo is translated into the form : value && constraints. value is the actual value of the division or modulo operation (e.g., the value of the division is the quotient). The format of the constraints can be read below.
